title: Episode 371: BET Awards 2022 Part 2
itunes:title: Episode 371: BET Awards 2022 Part 2
description:
On this weeks episode of Lip Service, we bring you Part 2 of our Media Room experience during the 2022 BET Awards show. We had the pleasure to sit down with MoneyBagg Yo, Bia, Neyo, Lakeyah, Bleu, Omaretta, Rob49, Tami Roman, Ghazi, Muni Long, DJ Drama & Seddy Hendrix.

*Disclaimer* This was recorded on June 25, 2022 - a lot has changed since then.

Enjoy!
